==[[Sumerian]]==
===Etymology===
Compound of '''''nam''''' (abstract prefix) + '''''ku/gu''''' (solid base, friend) + '''''li''''' (beer pot, true measure).

===Noun===
'''namguli''' (nam-gu5-li)

# [[friendship]]

